        "timestamp": "2019-04-08 12:13:38.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nIn fact the changes in patch 2 may not be correct for the latest version of Eclipse, as this causes the line indentation to be 8 spaces (2 times 4). The Google style guide states \"Indent continuation lines at least +4 spaces\".\nIt probably makes sense for the ONAP standards to explicitly state how many spaces to indent.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
