        "timestamp": "2019-04-08 13:36:43.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nI think that many license headers are using javadoc format (leading /** line) rather than just a java comment (leading /* line). With that minor change, the formatter will skip reformatting that section.",
        "patchset_number": 2
